        "Description": "A Chameleos has shown itself\u2014\r\nhmmm...no. A Chameleos has\r\nappeared\u2014*sigh* A Chameleos\r\nhas been spot\u2014We know it\u0027s out\r\nthere! Go hunt the cursed thing\r\nbefore it unleashes toadal chaos!\r\nNow, hop to it-to it!",
